    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance for Class II devices at MRL 2. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and supporting the relative hemolysis index comparison (RH < 1) against the predicate device.",
